{"title":"诗传单","authors":["张志民","夏自安"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":8,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗传单"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会上他说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望大家能点一点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的问题该怎么谈？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上了几岁年纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头脑实在有点儿“乱”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会后他想——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们掌握的材料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看来还不到一半，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那第七、八、九方案，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能瞒还是瞒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感情  张志民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他检讨——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些个言论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是一时“冲动”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是个“红脸汉子”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑瓜子好热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇事最爱动“感情”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的“说明”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该作如下更正："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是个白脸汉子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对反革命十分热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对人民实在没感情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛀木虫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏自安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛀木虫，嗡嗡嗡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴巴长的光打洞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬坏几多好门窗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛀烂新屋多少栋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑灭它，齐动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捣毁巢穴灭尽种；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派分子不悔改"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命运就像蛀木虫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载“江西日报”）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}